<html>
    <head>
        <title>my pet page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: arial , sans-serif;
            background-color: lightyellow;
            padding: 65px 30px 30px 30px;
            min-height: 1800px;
        }
        h1, h2 {color: darkorange;}
        .top-bar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: darkorange;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 20px;
        }
        .list-item {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid darkorange;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .special-note {
            position: relative;
            left: 30px;
            background-color: gold;
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }
        .pet-card {
            position: relative;
            background-color: white;
            border: 3px solid darkorange;
            padding: 15px 25px;
        }
        .badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 8px;
            right: 8px;
            background-color: forestgreen;
            color: white;
        }
        .section-lable {
            position: sticky;
            top: 55px;
            background-color: darkorange;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 15px 0 8px;
        }
    </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="top-bar">my pet page-buddy the labrodog</div>
        <h1>meet buddy</h1>
        <h2>relatives</h2>
        <p>this note shifts right from its normal spot.</p>
        <div class="special-note">pet of the month!</div>
        <h2>absolute</h2>
        <p>the badge is pinned to the corner of the card.</p>
        <div class="pet-card">
            <p>buddy-labrador, 2 years</p>
            <div class="badge">adopted</div>
        </div>
        <h2>sticky</h2>
        <p>scroll down- the lable locks at the top!</p>
        <div class="section-lable">more pets are available</div>
        <div class="list-item">luna - poodle , 1 year</div>
        <div class="list-item">max- german shepherd,3years</div>
        <div class="list-item">daisy- beagle, 4 years</div>
        <div class="list-item">rockey- golden retriever , 2 years</div>
        <div class="list-item">bella- border collie, 1 years</div>
        <div class="list-item">charlie- shih tzu, 5 years</div>
        <div class="list-item">coco- husky, 3 years</div>
        <div class="list-item">milo- tabby cat, 2 years</div>
    </body>
</html>